>\n<br />\n宜家政府個數字都計哂出黎<br />\n最快要2045年個建屋數字先可以追得上人口增長<br />\n比個上帝做都係咁<br />\n除非強行滅少人口<br />\n<br />\n即係簡單講, 你班賤民等到2045年先啦<br />\n到時一國兩制都就快完, 仲使CARE 你班賤民咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2374b60d1242dbbe41e087523f0486a2931cef94","tid":510740,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:07:19.000Z","msg":"唔係生不逢時，係唔識變通"},{"pid":"413db05d7ba5034ee6f6a4493f1732594ad8f401","tid":510740,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:08:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94ef49b1fe6b97c12a1da166154540b1c3aa8c10","tid":510740,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實全球大城市普遍現場嚟 唔好講到得香港至會發生。</blockquote>香港係特別嚴重<br />\n因為同時俾個獨裁大國殺雞取卵</blockquote><br />\n又搵籍口。你地香港人自己反對8萬5。關內地咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>之後講返要再起啦<br />\n係港共阻撚住</blockquote><br />\n又屈港共。係地產商同私樓反對。近排有單新聞起ive都反對。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起ive會培養d乜人出來？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人就係咁一味睇學歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />建制就多高學歷人士。唔怪得港島d人投建制多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n弱智<br />\n<br />\n唔睇學歷睇乜？<br />\n<br />\n有得比你揀讀ive定大學？<br />\n<br />\n弱智ive仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6fe38d5a051d62960d88e3252eab17ce99a0653","tid":510740,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"413db05d7ba5034ee6f6a4493f1732594ad8f401","tid":510740,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:08:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:14:19.000Z","msg":"因為港中殖民政府自1984英中聯合聲明開始限制賣地, 到97後一樣無搞好囉"},{"pid":"404dd079782d565b824fe